<div id="content" class="backgrnd4"><div id="right"><div id="box6"><h2 class="backgrnd12"><span class="text1">Proceedings of the Seventh Conference on Innovative Applications of Artificial Intelligence</span></h2><div class="content"><p><i>Sponsored by the Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence</i></p> <p><b>Edited by Jan Aikins and Howard Shrobe</b></p><p>August 20&ndash;23, 1995, Montreal, Quebec. Published by The AAAI Press, Menlo Park, California. <a href="../../Press/Proceedings/iaai95.php">This proceedings is also available in book and CD format.</a></p><p><b>Please Note:</b> Abstracts are linked to individual titles, and will appear in a separate browser window. Full-text versions of the papers are linked to the abstract text. Access to full text may be restricted to AAAI members. PDF file sizes may be large!</p><hr /><h3 class="left">Contents</h3><p class="left">IAAI-95 Program Committee / v</p><p class="left">AAAI Organization / vi</p><p class="left">Preface / 1</p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-001.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Equation and Knowledge Based Generative Gear Design System</a> / 4<br /><i>Karon Barber and Matthew Orel, General Motors Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-002.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">SABRE</a> / 24<br /><i>William C. Branley, Jr. and Earnest D. Harris, U.S. Army ArtificialIntelligence Center</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-003.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The GE Compliance Checker: A Generic Tool for Assessing Mortgage LoanResale Requirements</a> / 29<br /><i>Sue Bynum, Robert Noble, and Cheri Todd, GE Capital Mortgage Corporation; Ben Bloom, Inference Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-004.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The Multimission VICAR Planner: Automated Image Processing for Scientific Data Analysis</a> / 41<br /><i>Steve A. Chien and Helen B. Mortensen, Jet Propulsion Laboratory, California Institute of Technology</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-005.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">GENIUS(TM) Automated Underwriting System: Combining Knowledge Engineering and Machine Learning to Achieve Balanced Risk Assessment</a> / 49<br /><i>David C. Golibersuch, GE Corporate Research and Development; Rebecca Towne and Cheryl A. Wiebe, GE Capital Mortgage Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-006.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Scheduling of Marine Resources in the Port of Singapore Authority: <br />ATotal Approach</a> / 62<br /><i>Goh Kwong Heng, Goh Kah Seng, Lye Chee Whye, Tan Puay Hwa, and Tay Eng Kiang, Port of Singapore Authority</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-007.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">IMPACT: Development and Deployment Experience of Network EventCorrelation Applications</a> / 70<br /><i>Gabriel Jakobson, Mark Weissman, and Shri Goyal, GTE LaboratoriesIncorporated</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-008.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">SAMS: Strategic Account Management System</a> / 77<br /><i>Howard Kleinert, Canon U.S.A., Inc. and Raj Rao, Inference Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-009.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">DAS: Intelligent Scheduling Systems for Shipbuilding</a> / 90<br /><i>Jae Kyu Lee, Kyoung Jun Lee, June Seok Hong, and Wooju Kim, Korea Advanced Institute of Science and Technology; Eun Young Kim, Soo Yeoul Choi, Ho Dong Kim, and Ok Ryul Yang, Daewoo Heavy Industries Ltd.; Hyung Rim Choi, Dong-A University</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-010.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">EPO: A Knowledge Based System for Wood Procurement Management</a> / 107<br /><i>Seppo Linnainmaa, Juha Savola, and Olli Jokinen, VTT Information Technology, Finland</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-011.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">AutoCell -- An Intelligent Cellular Mobile Network Management System</a> /114<br /><i>Chee-Meng Low and You-Tong Tan, Information Technology Institute, Singapore; Soo-Yong Choo and Sie-Hung Lau, Singapore Telecom; Soo-Meng Tay, Singapore Telecom MobileLink</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-012.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">PCE: Generating Business Plans for New Products</a> / 125<br /><i>Don Palese, International Business Machines and Elizabeth Wall Ralston, Inference Corporation</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-013.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Automated Consultation for the Diagnosis of InterplanetaryTelecommunications</a> / 136<br /><i>A. G. Quan, U. M. Schwuttke, J. S. Herstein, J. S. Spagnuolo, and S. Burleigh, Jet Propulsion Laboratory, California Institute of Technology</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-014.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Experience with the Development and Deployment of <br />Expert Systems inAgriculture</a> / 146<br /><i>Ahmed A. Rafea, Sayed El-Azhari, Iman Ibrahim, Soliman Edres, and Mostafa Mahmoud, Ministry of Agriculture and Land Reclamation, Egypt</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-015.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The FinCEN Artificial Intelligence System: Identifying Potential MoneyLaundering from Reports of Large Cash Transactions</a> / 156<br /><i>Ted E. Senator, Henry G. Goldberg, Jerry Wooton, Matthew A. Cottini, A.F. Umar Khan, Christina D. Klinger, Winston M. Llamas, Michael P. Marrone, and Raphael W.H. Wong, U.S. Department of the Treasury</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-016.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Development of Self-Maintenance Photocopiers</a> / 171<br /><i>Yoshiki Shimomura and Sadao Tanigawa, Mita Industrial Co., Ltd., Japan; Yasushi Umeda and Tetsuo Tomiyama, The University of Tokyo</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1995/iaai95-017.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">AGETS MBR: An Application of Model-Based Reasoning to Gas TurbineDiagnostics</a> / 181<br /><i>Howard A. Winston and Robert T. Clark, United Technologies Research Center; Gene Buchina, United Technologies - Pratt &amp; Whitney Government Engine and Space Propulsion</i></p></div></div></div><div id="left">
